content:
Mr. Gary C. Peters, from the State of Michigan, called the Senate to order at  930 a.m.
Adjournment
Under the authority of the order of Friday, August 13, 2021, at  930 a.m. the ACTING PRESIDENT pro tempore declared the Senate adjourned, under its order of Friday, August 13, 2021, until  9 a.m. on Friday, August 20, 2021.
